 * ADVANCED ESP32 FLIGHT CONTROLLER
 * Complete solution for quadcopter/drone with:
 * - MPU6050 (6-DOF IMU)
 * - BMP280 (Barometric altitude)
 * - NRF24L01 (RC receiver link)
 * - 4x Brushless Motors with ESC control
 * 
 * Features:
 * - PID stabilization (Roll, Pitch, Yaw)
 * - Altitude hold
 * - Failsafe with auto-land
 * - Real-time telemetry
 * - Arming/disarming sequence
 * - Battery monitoring
 * - Data logging capability
